{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 275674, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "朝鲜不搞军事发展早都被平推了", "timestamp": 1598081444, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我个人觉得这条路线现在看起来很差劲，但是二十年后不好说。", "timestamp": 1598081575, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275683, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "朝鲜领导人不是在维护国家安全，而是在维护金家统治", "timestamp": 1598081669, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275684, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实朝鲜的经济出问题主要是在苏联垮了以后没大腿了，先军政治本身就是一种维稳手段，但是长期这样子恐怕受利的只有金家王朝", "timestamp": 1598081686, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275685, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 发展核武器威慑外国，保证了政权无法被外部势力颠覆，闭关锁国对内极权洗脑，保证了政权无法从内部被推翻。", "timestamp": 1598081741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275690, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 在这种情况下，就算内部发生政变导致了领导人的非正常更替，整个国家的体制也不会有丝毫变化。对朝鲜民众来说都一样", "timestamp": 1598081922, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275691, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "yysy 如果不是70年代后美国为了制衡苏联而接近中国以及改革开放初期的蜜月期，我国是不是也会这样孤立", "timestamp": 1598081926, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 如果没有改革开放，我国估计在第三波民主化浪潮中被一波带走咯", "timestamp": 1598081977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275700, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯 third wave确实也是当时大势所趋", "timestamp": 1598082084, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275701, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 就这么二极管？维护金家统治、维护朝鲜安全就满足排中律？", "timestamp": 1598082091, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275705, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: ？", "timestamp": 1598082192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275707, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 问题是在这种威权体制下除了免于外部入侵的安全有了别的也真没啥了吧", "timestamp": 1598082199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275709, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这时候就要呼叫一波#18077的dz", "timestamp": 1598082268, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275711, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 金政府被推平不等于朝鲜被推平。", "timestamp": 1598082367, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275735, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "金当局完蛋的话，我看韩国很乐意北进统一的。因为从朴正熙时代的南北共同声明就表明了南北应当统一", "timestamp": 1598082976, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275741, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: emmm我倒不这么认为，韩国真愿意接手这么一个烂摊子吗？韩国纳税人愿意花钱帮朝鲜建设吗？", "timestamp": 1598083100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 可能以前韩国愿意吧 现在民间给脱北者发生活费都不愿意", "timestamp": 1598083937, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275768, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这属于某种民族情绪，不论是保守派还是民主派，在自己手上完成统一永远是一件大好事。当然很有可能韩国会弄一个北方维持政府有序的恢复生产然后合并，朝鲜地区有着丰富的矿产资源+大量的劳动力，运用得好的好只会成为助力", "timestamp": 1598084049, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275776, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53441, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 是的，但是短期内对韩国经济和民众的负担还是很大的，不知道他们愿不愿意负担", "timestamp": 1598084288, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 53441, "reply": 19, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#政治相关\n不难想象，朝鲜领导人对军事力量和开发核武器的高度重视，也是基于稳固国内政权和维护领导人权威的政治考虑。但是，以损害经济发展和人民生活水平提高为代价发展军事力量，同时对外炫耀武力，究竟是有利于国家安全还是损害国家安全？", "timestamp": 1598081385, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782608, "url": "", "vote": {}}}